===Proper Noun===
{{Wikipedia}}
'''[[Darth]] Vader'''

#(''Star Wars'') Born in 41 [[BBY]] and died in 4 [[ABY]], the Dark Lord of the Sith and brutal apprentice to Darth Sidious.  In 19 BBY, [[Anakin Skywalker]] was dubbed Darth Vader when he turned to the dark side of the Force. His face, as it appears in [[Return of the Jedi]], resembles a hard-boiled [[egg]].

